{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MS03_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x3e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1010,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I just remembered that I have to buy some more synthesis ingredients."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1011,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure I'll need medicine, one way or another, from now on. But, I don't have that much money..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1012,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, maybe I need to look for jobs around here, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1013,
            "msg_string": "Let's see, I currently have... Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1014,
            "msg_string": "I-I don't have it! Where's my wallet!? Hrgh, I must've dropped it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1015,
            "msg_string": "Wh-Wh-Wh-What should I do!? What am I supposed to do at a time like this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x34fb,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, miss, are you in trouble?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x34fc,
            "msg_string": "Oh! Aren't you that weird girl from before?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x34fd,
            "msg_string": "Don't call me weird! You're in trouble, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x80,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x34fe,
            "msg_string": "I'll help you, so just tell me what's wrong."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x34ff,
            "msg_string": "W-Well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1019,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I was thinking about how I needed to go shopping, and then about how I needed to find work..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x101a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "So I went to check how much I had,<CR>and I couldn't find it anywhere!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x101b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay, that totally didn't make any sense. Just calm down a bit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x101c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay...I'll calm down.<CR>I think I dropped my wallet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x101d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Your wallet? Hmm, I see...<CR>So, you're clumsy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3505,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "From how you looked before, you were probably spacing out, and dropped it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x101f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ergh, yeah... Maybe you're right..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1020,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What should I do now?<CR>Who should I talk to?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3508,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, you're in luck!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1022,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Even though I dropped my wallet?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x350a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yup, cuz searching for lost items is my forte."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1024,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I'll find it in no time with my magic!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x350c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "M-Magic? Well, whatever the case, please find it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x350d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Leave it to me! Okay then, hmm!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x350e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What? Your hand...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1028,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What do you mean, \"What?\" Payment!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1029,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Jeez, you're slow on the uptake.<CR>Pay in advance. 50 Cole!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x102a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh, you're charging me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x102b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Of course. This is how I support myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3513,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "So, you go around finding things for people? How admirable for someone as small as you to be working already."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x102d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "That's not all. In a town this big,<CR>a lot of people have problems..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x102e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And I just use my magic on the down-low to solve them easily."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x102f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I see. That's great!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1030,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I end up making good money. If you need money, why don't you try it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1033,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "E-Enough of this talk, my payment!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1034,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, right. About that, everything I own is in my lost wallet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1035,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "So, I have...zero money on me right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1036,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You're so clumsy. You should carry at least two wallets..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1037,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And, that's a minimum precaution."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1038,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* I don't know anything about these things. I'll do that from now on..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1039,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Fiiine, it's your first time,<CR>so I'll do this one for free!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x351f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Really? *sigh* Thank you very much. Then if you would, please."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x103b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay, okay, leave it to me...<CR>Umm, where did I put it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x103c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Huh? Was it here? Or here...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x103d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, here it is! Here you go!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x103e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x103f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What do you mean, \"Huh?\"<CR>This is yours, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3525,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Y-Yes, it is. But why...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1041,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It was on the ground over there a few moments ago. It's freshly picked up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1043,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Awww, I was gonna look for the owner of that lost wallet and get money out of them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1044,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But, this time is a special case.<CR>Make sure you thank me a lot!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3529,
            "msg_string": "(She's only a child, but she's already working. How admirable...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1047,
            "msg_string": "(Maybe I should look for something that I can do...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "People in town have various problems. By solving those problems, you can receive tokens of appreciation or gain trust."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Most of the problems people in town have are things that can be solved by giving them synthesized items."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Some problems may even specify material items or item categories, not necessarily a specific item."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "By satisfying certain conditions with the items you give them, it'll be easier to solve their problems."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "It's up to your play-style to either solve a problem by meeting the conditions through quality or quantity."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "There are time limits to the rewards. If you go over the limit, your reward will be affected."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Conversations in town can be viewed again by accessing the Notes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "If you are unsure of what item to prepare, check out the Notes."
        }
    ]
}